re-read what i said. I said you cant change the length that the songs LASTS, not CASTS.  songs last 3 ticks, or 18 seconds.  Now if you were able to gain 10% song duration this is 19.8 seconds, which is 4 ticks.  The game clock works every 6 seconds when it reduced the time left on an affect.  So unless there was a way to gain full tick cycles it's pointless.  They could give an aa that give 10/20/30 % more duration, but it would still be 4 ticks.  You would need at least a 34% increase to go to 5. </span></td>
